{
  "stem": "769.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I started to make money there, and every day I went to the train with ice cream, in the morning to the evening, once and twice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I sold it and I called, one ruble an ice cream, one ruble!",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I got three assortments of ice cream-- like vanilla and red, they make it with syrup, and some other kind with some walnuts.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after, when the war came, started the war-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my-- the-- I remember my sister and my brother told me, take it how much you have.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If what you have, take it and run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, why you not?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got so much money, we're going to come, our mother, and his parents, they have so much money-- they have gold and diamonds in there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To bring it home, they will save the mother in a-- and they didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the moment when we run away, the last train, I went deep to deep Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The last train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they wait there in the moment when the last train went, the Ukrainian people, rounded up all Jews there, and they killed them before the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before the-- ha, I notice everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the war, when I went home, I have to go through the same city, Zdolbunov.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because Zdolbunov is the key train station, what exchange the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when I came from Russia, and I wanted to go to Poland, I have to go through the station Zdolbunov, the same thing, to change from the platform to another train.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Knowing the city, and working on the station, you know, when I sold the ice cream, I know every door and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Never mind it's bombed-- or-- I know everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
